TOUCH 
to deal with timestamps and empty file creations

# touch file_name : create an empty file as specified 
if the file is already avialable it will update the timestamp of that file

# touch .file_name : creates an empty hidden file

# touch {1..10}.txt : creates 100 text files 

# touch -t YYYYMMDDHHMM file_name : to modify the timestamp of the file

# touch -m file_name : to change the timestamp to the modification time

# touch -a file_name : to change the timestamp to the access time



